OL,13,Fopposed locally is dwarfed by three
OL,14,Fmore solar farms which developers
OL,15,Fwould like for the Marsh - they are
OL,16,Fcurrently in early planning stages.
OL,18,FThe St Mary in the Marsh project will
OL,19,Fproduce 16 megawatts of power - and
OL,20,Fcover 100 acres.
